    <h2>Introduction</h2>
        <body>
            <p>Welcome to the net-api tool.</p>
            <p>This tool provides a REST API interface with network devices so that structured data can be returned and queried.</p>
            <p>By exposing REST APIs to network devices, both network and non-network operators can gain access to the configuration and state of the network.</p>
